1
00:00:00,375 --> 00:00:06,791
I am Ahmad from the
town of Tabqa, 25 years old

2
00:00:08,375 --> 00:00:17,833
I was imprisoned by ISIS in
2016, during Ramadan, for 33 days

3
00:00:22,083 --> 00:00:28,916
They put me in their prison for 33 days, during which I
was tortured unjustly. I had not committed any offense

4
00:00:30,291 --> 00:00:35,916
Because of one of my friends who had committed
some wrongdoings, I used to hang out at his place

5
00:00:36,083 --> 00:00:42,500
I left his house and he told me he had something entrusted to
him and asked me to bring it on my way from the town of Mansoura

6
00:00:43,291 --> 00:00:49,333
I went and they caught me there. I was standing in
front of a shop when a car came and masked men got out

7
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:55,125
Only their eyes were visible and they wore
black. They arrested me immediately by name

8
00:00:55,666 --> 00:01:00,833
They put me in the trunk of the car, locked it, and asked me,
where is Abdul Latif? Of course with beating and humiliation

9
00:01:02,208 --> 00:01:10,166
Punches to my stomach and back. They locked the trunk
on me and went looking for my friend Abdul Latif

10
00:01:11,625 --> 00:01:20,500
Neither of us knew what the issue was. They took us
and put us in the Finance building in the town of Tabqa

11
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:24,375
In a basement, in a solitary cell,
and of course they separated us

12
00:01:25,083 --> 00:01:29,750
They also brought in someone else we had been
with the night before, named Nasser al-Ammar

13
00:01:30,666 --> 00:01:37,541
They took us and searched for him for an hour and a half to
two hours. He had fled because he knew he had done something

14
00:01:37,958 --> 00:01:45,916
They brought him and put him with us on the <i>balingo</i> [hoist
for suspension] and kept us in prison for three days

15
00:01:46,541 --> 00:01:53,875
Then they brought us to Bourj [Tower] Prison, to the basement. Of
course we were blindfolded and did not know where we were going

16
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:59,375
But since we were from the area, we knew where they
were taking us. We felt we were in Bourj Prison

17
00:02:00,166 --> 00:02:06,750
We went down and they put us in a dark place. The lights
stayed on around the clock. We could not tell night from day

